folder: Fresh Meadow Lane & Auburndale Lane, Queens, NY
original_title: Queens: Fresh Meadow Lane - Auburndale Lane
text:
Fresh Meadow Lane, north side, east of Auburndale Lane, showing the J. Lawrence house of 1873. In 1909 it was the property of Dewitt and Lott.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
